article_title: Franken, Klobuchar have questions for Comcast-Time Warner

article_metadata.description: WASHINGTON — Both Minnesota senators say they have questions for Comcast and Time Warner before the two media giants are allowed to merge.The only difference: Amy Klobuchar is taking a look, while Al Franken is taking aim.

og.description: WASHINGTON — Sen. Amy Klobuchar is taking a look — and Sen. Al Franken, taking aim — at a proposed merger between the cable giants.
